    "updated_at": "2015-01-03T00:07:54Z",
    "body": "> Since there's hardly a reason to not support \"dark mode\" on the menubar i have enabled it by default. \n\nThis will break people who don't create an image specifically designed to be a template, can you make `false` the default instead and submit a PR? This is a good fix to have in the main build and it should be pretty easy to make the parameter optional\n"
